data.system_settings: Windows 8.1 64 bit (wont be reproduceable on web as control+tab and control+shift+tab change tabs in most browsers)
data.expected_result: Discord switches to the next server (or wraps around to last DM or friends/game tab). Discord switches down if control+tab was pressed and up if control+shift+tab was pressed.
